dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours. "Administrative boundaries revised to May, 1950". Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is included in companion volume. "C.B.H. 28016-Wt-2023-Dd.7148-1750-7/56." Includes index to gazetteer reference, and diagram showing the magnetic variation 1947. This topographic map shows the territorial boundaries, provincial and district administrative divisions, railways, three classes of roads, and aeronautical information. Include index to gazetteer reference, and diagram showing the magnetic variation 1947.
dct_publisher_sm: Dar-es-Salaam : Dept. of Lands and Surveys, 1950.
